    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Rites or sacraments administered as a reaffirmation of a particular religious faith. Examples are the rites administered to baptized persons in various Christian churches, intended to bestow a special grace upon the recipient that confirms or strengthens their Christian faith.</Note_Text>
